headline: Travelers Financial Solutions Supports Beautifi Financial Solutions' Launch of New Underwriting Facility to Expand Equipment Financing Access for Clinics
summary: VANCOUVER, BC / ACCESS Newswire / January 12, 2026 / Beautifi Financial Solutions (Beautifi) today announced the launch of a new underwriting facility designed to expand access to commercial equipment financing for aesthetic, medical, and dental clinics. ...

headline: 3 Large-Cap Stocks Worth Investigating
summary: Large-cap stocks have the power to shape entire industries thanks to their size and widespread influence. With such vast footprints, however, finding new areas for growth is much harder than for smaller, more agile players.
